Sentencas: NiO-Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95-BaCe0.8Y0.2O3-delta (NiO-GDC-BCY) anode based solid oxide fuel cell was fabricated, in which the composite powders of NiO-GDC and BCY were synthesized by solution combustion method and mixed by physical mixing.
Titulo: NiO-GDC-BCY composites as an anode for SOFC

Sentencas: In the present case, the composite anode material was prepared with varying amount of GDC (2 wt% to 8 wt%) with respect to NiO (38 wt% to 32 wt%) and studied their structural, morphological and electrical properties.
Titulo: NiO-GDC-BCY composites as an anode for SOFC

Sentencas: The single cell was fabricated comprising NiO-GDC-BCY (34: 6: 60) anode, LSCF (cathode) and BaCe0.8Y0.2O3-delta (electrolyte).
Titulo: NiO-GDC-BCY composites as an anode for SOFC

Sentencas: The open circuit voltage was measured in hydrogen and biogas atmospheres.
Titulo: NiO-GDC-BCY composites as an anode for SOFC
